{"tid":257260,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"專家：數據或異常一致　署方起疑","createTime":"2017-05-25T06:41:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-25T07:56:25.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c68bd139d356168a92f28254458803d0adbc726f","tid":257260,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T06:41:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20032973&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170525\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20032973%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170525&d=3%2Fyb9fo0OzuLUwrjyftdmr%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=136b3554\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20032973%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170525&h=e2bf35a7\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20032973&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170525</a><br />\n<br />\n專家：數據或異常一致　署方起疑<br />\n<br />\n要聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n港珠澳橋爆出混凝土磚測試造假醜聞。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】土木工程拓展署去年中檢查混凝土磚測試報告時發現不尋常，但無具體交代案情。工程師學會理事劉志健分析，一般做混凝土磚壓力測試，每塊磚硬度有差異，涉嫌造假的實驗室以強力石屎磚和金屬校準柱頂包做測試，得出數據會較一致，硬度亦會超出設計參數，或因此引起署方懷疑。<br />\n此外，測試報告會紀錄磚塊裂紋，若以金屬代替磚塊受壓，裂紋形態可能不同。<br />\n<br />\n大型工程委託多個實驗室<br />\n<br />\n劉志健續稱，較全面的測試報告包括測試混凝土磚相片，難以理解涉案實驗室竟以金屬校準柱頂包做測試，「有啲初步報告未有相，一個全面報告應該係有相，（磚塊）壓前壓後嘅樣，如果唔係我點去了解壓完後破壞情況係點呢？」<br />\n有資深實驗室人員分析，政府即使已委託實驗室檢測混凝土磚，亦會不定期自行做抽檢。大型工程會委託多於一個實驗室，政府可要求兩間實驗室交叉測試混凝土磚，或因此發現不尋常地方。很多實驗室都已安裝閉路電視，確保實驗過程留下紀錄，若大規模造假，閉路電視或會紀錄犯罪經過。<br />\n■記者潘柏林<br />\n<br />\n97年主權移交至今，香港前進還是倒退？「蘋果」與你細數廿載風雨。<br />\n【回歸二十年】專頁：&nbsp;<a href=\"http://hksar20.appledaily.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhksar20.appledaily.com.hk&d=3%2Fyb9fo0OzuLUwrjyftdmr%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=559d06af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hksar20.appledaily.com.hk</a>￼<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n嘉科至少接10政府合約　涉3.7億<br />\n<br />\n要聞&nbsp;8小時前<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n路政署測試僅得表面數據<br />\n<br />\n要聞&nbsp;8小時前<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n港珠澳橋造假醜聞　總承建商顧問難卸責政府今開記者會交代<br />\n<br />\n要聞&nbsp;8小時前"},{"pid":"406d8506252f5a04e3c623367e2a82b31528e0ba","tid":257260,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T06:42:06.000Z","msg":"港珠澳橋爆出混凝土磚測試造假醜聞。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170525/large/0524garym5101.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170525%2Flarge%2F0524garym5101.jpg&h=ed04379a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e1fc94051e71514247e69c098d7aa374694b05f2","tid":257260,"uid":71441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T07:09:59.000Z","msg":"this is china.jpg"},{"pid":"7f0d3b27c64f459ec7bc9f3657578bc313865914","tid":257260,"uid":36287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T07:11:19.000Z","msg":"中學生都識作啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4389e1584528ee510fcd74d9be0fc1064264883e","tid":257260,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T07:12:26.000Z","msg":"真係十年唔冧都偷笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a3383bb0fce27f8a0c7feb0583748b373300131","tid":257260,"uid":66822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T07:15:40.000Z","msg":"即係香港都有豆腐渣?"},{"pid":"a1a5743bd3a4318f0b572cd81f1c660e3bcc0abf","tid":257260,"uid":33039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T07:33:59.000Z","msg":"出貓唔好太高分"},{"pid":"c7ee3c8f1bd2aab080b836fd810d4debc04afcb7","tid":257260,"uid":51215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T07:35:32.000Z","msg":"出貓唔好出得咁低能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e92cc8682eaa94fc7919ad3bddbe9682913a4819","tid":257260,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T07:38:40.000Z","msg":"最好d大官行果陣即冧 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4473427dc4620ddb030f96bad7ea359000a14fe4","tid":257260,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T07:41:02.000Z","msg":"細細個作數據都識用COMMON SENSE作"},{"pid":"5f8ebad91a4450276b7e83aac4e8847adb688782","tid":257260,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T07:47:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細細個作數據都識用COMMON SENSE作</blockquote><br />\n有無例子 ?"},{"pid":"d0846fa8484ae41cf1ec39d2e77666c681dd4e05","tid":257260,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T07:50:38.000Z","msg":"塌嗰時，共媒會話反對派拉布搞到唔夠錢買真材實料。"},{"pid":"5899248276e60ef7b9a363be022fb9d65809b8d2","tid":257260,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T07:56:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}